 Should have constructed a multistoried office building / hospital building/ institutional building/ commercial buildings having minimum built-up area 20000 SQM at Government/Semi Government / PSU / Private Organization of National / International importance.

"Similar nature of Work Requirements: Minimum Single work of similar nature for Maintenance, operation and Housekeeping, of large modern office/ institutional building /hospital and  commercial  buildings of 20000 SQM in Govt. / Semi Govt. / PSU / Private firm during last 5 years ending March-2021 are eligible to participate. 
OR
Should have constructed a multistoried office building/hospital building/ institutional building /commercial buildings of 20000 sqm with HVAC/AHU/Air Conditioner, STP, Lift, Sub-Station, Electrical HT/LT work, Fire-Fighting work, Landscaping, PHE & Drainage work, UG water Tank, Anti-Termite treatment, Networking Work, PA System, Data system and the same work has been completed/installed. 
"			The Experience certificate should be issued by the authority not less than the rank of EE. In case of Private sector work experience, evaluated certificate by Retired officer of rank not below of Executive Engineer or by Nationalized Bank/ Nationalized Insurance Corporation / Income tax registered valuer is required as per BCD Bihar letter no 3284 dated 05.05.2009

Minimum financial Requirements: Minimum ATO (Annual Turnover) of any one year during last five audited financial years from comprehensive maintenance must not be less than 05 Crore. Tenderer shall submit last five years audited financial statement (Profit Loss Statement) duly attested / certified by CA.			Audit report of 2016 to March 2021,to be indexed at the rate of 8% for a year.
